metadata.name: The Degenaissance
metadata.description:
A revolution is here.
One you are an essential part of.
Our culture is changing.
We can all feel it.
Now is the time to lead that change.

Today...

We announce that 50 billion $LIT has been bequeathed to the $LIT community to fund and administer a Cultural DAO.
Designed to lead the arts & entertainment into the future.
With the world's first cultural currency.

*Degenaissance by rata_yonqui*
